al/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T22:52:08.000Z","msg":"佢講到咁我諗佢都好撚清楚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過盡人事啦<br />\n但條友其實都有啲神神化化咁，疑似撒但教徒，又話香港係咩神秘學中心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86825cba00318cb5872ce82a28719525c67002b4","tid":720304,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T22:57:42.000Z","msg":"佢寫咗段日文<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcb70524a0b54fa14dae6995f91378fd0a70721","tid":720304,"uid":49136,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T22:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A7%8B%E6%98%8E%E5%B7%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25A7%258B%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B7%259E&d=6o5J3rfpv8I1lZsuW3vT1V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=560be581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A7%8B%E6%98%8E%E5%B7%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8C%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B0%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BD%2597%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258C%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B1%25BB%25E5%258F%2591%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%25B0%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=6o5J3rfpv8I1lZsuW3vT1V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=1145950a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8C%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B0%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n烏拉爾地區嘅秋明州人類發展指數係俄羅斯第二高<br />\n經濟增長都高於俄國<br />\n<br />\n有冇問佢係因為種族（唔係指官方定義）、文化、語言定經濟而想獨立？"},{"pid":"56018de886e9ac5691e07a427be686bcaf7c1c4b","tid":720304,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislik